---
// Footer completo para Taberna El Rinconcillo
---

<footer class="bg-gray-900 text-white">
  <div
    class="w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8 sm:py-10 lg:py-12"
  >
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 sm:gap-8">
      <!-- Información del Restaurante -->
      <div class="space-y-3 sm:space-y-4">
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
          <div
            class="w-6 h-6 sm:w-8 sm:h-8 bg-[#FF8833] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-3 h-3 sm:w-4 sm:h-4 text-white"
              fill="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
            >
              <path
                d="M3 4a1 1 0 011-1h12a1 1 0 110 2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1zm0 4a1 1 0 011-1h12a1 1 0 110 2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1zm0 4a1 1 0 011-1h12a1 1 0 110 2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold">Taberna El Rinconcillo</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base">
          Un acogedor rincón en el corazón de Terque donde la tradición y el
          sabor se encuentran.
        </p>
        <div class="flex space-x-2 sm:space-x-3"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Enlaces Rápidos -->
      <div class="space-y-3 sm:space-y-4">
        <h4 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-[#FF8833]">
          Enlaces Rápidos
        </h4>
        <ul class="space-y-1 sm:space-y-2">
          <li>
            <a
              href="/"
              class="text-gray-300 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300 text-sm sm:text-base"
              >Inicio</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="/Carta.pdf"
              class="text-gray-300 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300 text-sm sm:text-base"
              >Nuestra Carta</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="/"
              class="text-gray-300 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300 text-sm sm:text-base"
              >Horarios</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="/"
              class="text-gray-300 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300 text-sm sm:text-base"
              >Opiniones</a
            >
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Información de Contacto -->
      <div class="space-y-3 sm:space-y-4">
        <h4 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-[#FF8833]">
          Contacto
        </h4>
        <div class="space-y-2 sm:space-y-3">
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-2 sm:space-x-3">
            <svg
              class="w-4 h-4 sm:w-5 sm:h-5 text-[#FF8833] mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"
              ></path>
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm sm:text-base">
                Plaza Constitución, 10
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm sm:text-base">
                04569 Terque, Almería
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 sm:space-x-3">
            <svg
              class="w-4 h-4 sm:w-5 sm:h-5 text-[#FF8833] flex-shrink-0"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm sm:text-base">+34 600 09 89 01</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 sm:space-x-3">
            <svg
              class="w-4 h-4 sm:w-5 sm:h-5 text-[#FF8833] flex-shrink-0"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M3 8l7.89 4.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm sm:text-base">
              tabernarinconcillo@outlook.es
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Horarios -->
      <div class="space-y-3 sm:space-y-4"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Línea divisoria -->
    <div class="border-t border-gray-700 mt-8 pt-8">
      <div
        class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center space-y-4 md:space-y-0"
      >
        <div class="text-gray-400 text-xs lg:*:text-sm">
          © 2024 Taberna El Rinconcillo. Todos los derechos reservados.
        </div>
        <div class="flex space-x-6 text-sm">
          <p>
            Designed & Developed by <a
              href="https://linkedin.com/in/ivan-mayoral-capel"
              target="_blank"
              class="text-yellow-400"
              rel="noopener noreferrer">Iván Mayoral Capel</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
